 
 images used 
 
 Mercury
 
 2k.Mercury.png
reduced data from
http://pds-imaging.jpl.nasa.gov/data/messenger/msgrmds_5001/MDR/

Venus 

2k.Venus.png
reduced and cleaned up data from magellan radar data 
http://pds-imaging.jpl.nasa.gov/volumes/magellan.html#mgnFMAP


2k.VenusNormal.png
produced using NMS for correct spherical mapping of the normals 
based on the data from
http://pds-imaging.jpl.nasa.gov/data/mgn-v-rdrs-5-gdr-emissivity-v1.0/mg_3002/


2k.VenusClouds.png
100% synthetic used "GaseousGiganticus.c" to create it 

The Earth

2k.Earth.png
based on the bluemarble2 data 
http://mirrors.arsc.edu/nasa/world_500m/

2k.EarthLights.png
derived from
https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/eog/viirs/download_ut_mos.html
and calibrated to 
https://www.ngdc.noaa.gov/eog/dmsp/download_radcal.html

2k.EarthNormal.png
produced using NMS for correct spherical mapping of the normals 
derived from "ds15_grd.zip"
https://topotools.cr.usgs.gov/gmted_viewer/gmted2010_global_grids.php

2k.EarthSpec.png
derived from the heightmap 

2k.EarthCloud.png

based on the 43200 x 21600 visable earth mapping
http://visibleearth.nasa.gov/view.php?id=57747



The Moon 

2k.MoonLRO-WAC.png
based on 
http://lroc.sese.asu.edu/data/LRO-L-LROC-5-RDR-V1.0/LROLRC_2001/DATA/BDR/WAC_GLOBAL/

2k.MoonNormalLRO_WAC.png
produced using NMS for correct spherical mapping of the normals
http://lroc.sese.asu.edu/data/LRO-L-LROC-5-RDR-V1.0/LROLRC_2001/DATA/SDP/WAC_GLD100/



Mars

2k.Mars.png
based on the older data from MSSS 
http://www.msss.com/mgcwg/mgm/

2k.MarsNormal.png
produced using NMS for correct spherical mapping of the normals
based on the 128 ppd Mola data
http://pds-geosciences.wustl.edu/missions/mgs/megdr.html


Phobos

Phobos.cmod 
shape file extracted from 
http://sbn.psi.edu/pds/resource/phobosshape.html
VO1_SA_VISA_VISB_5_PHOBOSSHAPE_V1_0.zip

2k.PhobosMap.png
derived from  "phobos_cyl_dlr_control.fit" 
http://sbn.psi.edu/pds/resource/stookemaps.html
MULTI-SA-MULTI-6-STOOKEMAPS-V2.0 


Deimos 

Deimos.low.bin.cmod
derived from "m2deimos.tab"
http://sbn.psi.edu/pds/resource/oshape.html
EAR_A_5_DDR_SHAPE_MODELS_V2_1.zip

2k.Deimos.png
based on "deimos_cyl_viking_mro.fit"
http://sbn.psi.edu/pds/resource/stookemaps.html
MULTI-SA-MULTI-6-STOOKEMAPS-V2.0 

























